            "margintopreadmob": 0,
            "marginbottomreadmob": 0,
            "main-text": "Knya’s 6sense Stethoscope: Precision meets style with a custom-engraved stethoscope for doctors - Built for daily performance.",
            "content-text-before": "<h2>Introduction:</h2><p>The stethoscope is one of the most recognizable symbols of the medical profession.</p>",
            "content-text": "<h2>Introduction:</h2><p>The stethoscope is one of the most recognizable symbols of the medical profession.</p><p>Introducing the Knya's 6sense Stethoscope, a high-performance diagnostic instrument meticulously engineered for discerning medical professionals like you. This isn't just a stethoscope; it's a precision tool designed to deliver superior acoustics, enabling you to capture subtle sounds with unparalleled clarity. Experience enhanced performance in every auscultation, leading to more accurate diagnoses and ultimately, improved patient care.<br/>Built with durability in mind, the Knya's 6sense Stethoscope is a reliable companion for your demanding practice. Its ergonomic design ensures comfort during extended use, making it an indispensable instrument for precise auscultation, day after day.</p><h2>Looking for the Best Stethoscope?</h2><p>The Knya's 6sense stands out with its advanced features and quality construction. For doctors and healthcare professionals who demand accuracy and reliability, the 6sense is a compelling choice. </p><h2>Make it Your Own: Engraved and Personalized Stethoscopes:</h2><p>Elevate your professional identity with our engraved stethoscope option. Add a personal touch with your name or initials, making your Knya 6sense truly unique. Explore our custom stethoscope services for a personalized instrument that reflects your dedication.</p><h2>Understanding Stethoscope Price:</h2><p>Investing in a high-quality stethoscope is an investment in your practice and your patients. The Knya 6sense offers exceptional value for its advanced acoustic performance and durability. Explore our pricing options to discover a stethoscope price that aligns with its superior quality.</p><h2> The Stethoscope for Doctors Who Demand Precision:</h2><p>The Knya 6sense is specifically designed with the needs of doctors in mind. Its advanced acoustic technology allows for confident diagnoses across various medical specialties.</p><h2>Your Personalized Diagnostic Tool:</h2><p>Beyond engraving, explore options for a truly personalized stethoscope with Knya. Choose from various colors and finishes to match your individual style and professional preference.<br/>Experience the difference with the Knya 6sense Stethoscope – where superior acoustics meet enhanced performance and lasting durability. Elevate your practice, one auscultation at a time.</p>",
            "read-more-text": "READ MORE",
            "read-less-text": "READ LESS",
            "back-img": "shopify://shop_images/Vector_e3c241a2-7b11-44f6-8e63-6dcca5fa809c.png"
          },
